sequenceDiagram
participant Client
participant Connection
participant Server
participant MessageHandler
participant NewsDatabase

Note over Server: serve_one(server, db)

Server->>Connection: waitForActivity()

Server->>Server: process_request()

Server->>MessageHandler: recvCode()

MessageHandler->>MessageHandler: recvCode()
MessageHandler->>MessageHandler: recvBytes()

MessageHandler->>Connection: read()

Server->>Server: switch(COM_GET_ART)

Server->>Server: handle_get_art(mh, db)

Server->>MessageHandler: recvIntParameter(ngId)
Server->>MessageHandler: recvIntParameter(aId)

Server->>NewsDatabase: getArticle(ngId, aId)
NewsDatabase-->>Server: GetArticleResult res

Server->>MessageHandler: sendCode(ANS_GET_ART)

alt article exists
    Server->>MessageHandler: sendCode(ANS_ACK)
    Server->>MessageHandler: sendStringParameter(title)
    Server->>MessageHandler: sendStringParameter(author)
    Server->>MessageHandler: sendStringParameter(text)
else newsgroup missing
    Server->>MessageHandler: sendCode(ANS_NAK)
    Server->>MessageHandler: sendCode(REE_NG_DOES_NOT_EXIST)
else
    Server->>MessageHandler: sendCode(ANS_NAK)
    Server->>MessageHandler: sendCode(REE_ART_DOES_NOT_EXIST)
end

Server->>MessageHandler: sendCode(ANS_END)

MessageHandler->>Connection: write bytes back
Connection-->>Client: response delivered